# Get Captcha Request
The final part of solving hcaptcha is the `getcaptcha` API.
When we plug everything we just did into this one API we should end up with the final solved JWT(Json Web Token) captcha token!

## Request
| URL | Method |
| - | - |
| https://hcaptcha.com/getcaptcha?s=91e4137f-95af-4bc9-97af-cdcedce21c8c | `POST` |

## Response

```json
{
    "c": {
        "type": "hsw",
        "req": "eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..b_ygUVUbcOvObiDHZt_QzThgmR6gxGsonvRo-vG20k8"
    },
    "pass": true,
    "generated_pass_UUID": "P0_eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..W7BIL_Sb2aj01o9g-L8lzGeE49u86MSP93j750bs9JY",
    "expiration": 120
}
```

If you get the generated_pass_UUID than congrats you have solved hcaptcha nad fucked Epic Games at the same time :0
